{
  "id": "long-ash-listening-test",
  "title": "Listening Bell",
  "nodes": {
    "start": {
      "conditions": {
        "flag": "heard-bell-docket-read"
      },
      "else": "sava-gate",
      "lines": [
        "The docket gives the pin order. A short pull will strike the tongue against the frame without ringing the chapel above."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Put your hand against the frame",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the apparatus still",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "sava-gate": {
      "conditions": {
        "flag": "heard-bell-sava-found"
      },
      "else": "unavailable",
      "lines": [
        "The copper pins lead from the bell frame to Sava's niche. Each has been filed to a different length."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Put your hand against the frame",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the apparatus still",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "unavailable": {
      "lines": [
        "A bell tongue hangs inside a frame of copper pins. Without the docket or a known subject, striking it would be guesswork."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Do not touch it",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "test-menu": {
      "lines": [
        "The bell tongue rests a finger's width from the copper frame. Every listening wire runs toward the sealed niche."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Strike the frame once",
          "conditions": {
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-test-first"
            ]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-test-first",
            "log": "The tongue touches copper. One movement travels through the floor from inside the niche."
          },
          "next": "first-result",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Strike a second time",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "heard-bell-test-first",
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-test-second"
            ]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-test-second"
          },
          "next": "second-trace",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Strike a third time",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "heard-bell-test-second",
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-test-third",
              "heard-bell-sava-quieted",
              "heard-bell-sava-killed"
            ]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": [
              "heard-bell-test-third",
              "heard-bell-sava-thawing"
            ],
            "log": "The third strike reaches the niche. A pale crack runs down its seal."
          },
          "next": "third-result",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Quiet the listening niche",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "heard-bell-test-second",
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-sava-quieted",
              "heard-bell-sava-killed"
            ]
          },
          "next": "quiet-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Take your hand from the frame",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "first-result": {
      "lines": [
        "The movement comes after the copper stops. It is too slow for an echo and too heavy for a loose stone."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Return to the bell tongue",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Stop the test",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "second-trace": {
      "conditions": {
        "traceMin": 1
      },
      "else": "second-medicine",
      "lines": [
        "The answer enters through your teeth instead of your ears. A man's voice holds inside the vibration.",
        "The bell below us rang first."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Return to the apparatus",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Stop the test",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "second-medicine": {
      "conditions": {
        "fieldRatings": {
          "medicine": 40
        }
      },
      "else": "second-host-signs",
      "lines": [
        "A breath draws through the sealed space. It starts before the bell tongue lands, then stops as if somebody is holding it."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Return to the apparatus",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Stop the test",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "second-host-signs": {
      "conditions": {
        "fieldRatings": {
          "hostSigns": 40
        }
      },
      "else": "second-clean",
      "lines": [
        "The movement begins before the strike. Whatever waits in the wall has learned the pull of your hand. It is anticipating the sound."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Return to the apparatus",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Stop the test",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "second-clean": {
      "lines": [
        "A measured vibration crosses the floor before the copper is quiet. It has the spacing of words, but no sound reaches the room."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Return to the apparatus",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Stop the test",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "third-result": {
      "lines": [
        "Dust falls from the niche in a thin line. Something behind the seal draws a full breath and turns its face toward the north wall."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Try to quiet it",
          "next": "quiet-menu",
          "close": false
        },
        {
          "label": "Step away from the bell",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "quiet-menu": {
      "lines": [
        "The docket marks four ways to stop a response. Three are written by wardens. Hessa's cadence is pressed into the register margins."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Set the containment pins in safe order",
          "conditions": {
            "fieldRatings": {
              "containment": 40
            }
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-sava-quieted",
            "log": "The pins take the strain one at a time. Sava's breathing slows until the wire lies still."
          },
          "close": true
        },
        {
          "label": "Recite the mortuary quieting office",
          "conditions": {
            "fieldRatings": {
              "doctrine": 40
            }
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-sava-quieted",
            "log": "The old office fixes breath to count and count to silence. The niche stops answering."
          },
          "close": true
        },
        {
          "label": "Use mortuary quieting salt",
          "conditions": {
            "items": {
              "mortuary-quieting-salt": 1
            }
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-sava-quieted",
            "inventory": {
              "requireAll": true,
              "remove": [
                {
                  "item": "mortuary-quieting-salt",
                  "count": 1
                }
              ]
            },
            "log": "Salt bites at the bell hinge and the niche seam. The movement below the stone eases."
          },
          "close": true
        },
        {
          "label": "Use Hessa's intact cadence",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "heard-bell-register-read",
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "heard-bell-register-damaged"
            ]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "heard-bell-sava-quieted",
            "log": "You keep Hessa's count and leave the last beat empty. Sava follows it into silence."
          },
          "close": true
        },
        {
          "label": "Do not attempt the quieting",
          "next": "test-menu",
          "close": false
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
